snippet.textDisplay:
Asha Bhosle Once Said in one of her Comments after Nabeel's performance "Pehla Nasha" in Sur Kshetra 


"Aap ki awaaz main waqai bohat taazgi hai aur alag kism ki awaaz hai aur aisi awaazain hamari film line ko chahiye, Asal main aaj kal chahiye kion ke love song ganey waley koi rahey nahi hain sub ooncha hi gatey rehtey hain jaisey waqai love song hota hai waisey ganey waley chahiyen".


She was Damn Right. Mahesh Bhatt Was also present in that Episode.

Waqai Ustaad log Ustaad hotey hain, parakh letey hain, bhaanp letey hain. Nabeel Shaukat Ali Way to Go My dear. God Bless.
